{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV","title":"OUDSCheckbox"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckbox"]}],"sections":[],"relationshi